Paper: hep-th/9907009

Date: 1999-07-02

Title: Pure Spinor Formalism for Conformal Fermion and Conserved Currents

Authors: Liu YuFen, MA ZhongQi and Hou BoYuan

Comments: 10 pages

Journal-ref: Commun.Theor.Phys. 31 (1999) 481-490

Pure spinor formalism and non-integrable exponential factors are used forconstructing the conformal-invariant wave equation and Lagrangian density formassive fermion. It is proved that canonical Dirac Lagrangian for massivefermion is invariant under induced projective conformal transformations.